Speaker 2: Yeah, I got Viagra here and I was wanting to cancel the order.

Speaker 2: Joseph Fugett.

Speaker 2: 423-300-4008.

Speaker 1: Alrighty, sir, I do see your VIP here getting that Viagra.

Speaker 2: You don't have to get it monthly.

Speaker 1: You don't have to get it every month, sir.

Speaker 2: Yeah, correct.

Speaker 1: Yeah, I can give you my number as well, my extension.

Speaker 2: You can call me, I can place them for you.

Speaker 1: All right, so the name is simply just going to be –

Speaker 2: Well, let me give you the phone number, too,

Speaker 1: because you're calling in from a different one.

Speaker 1: All right.

Speaker 2: And my name is Quinn and the extension is going to be 0035.

Speaker 1: 0035, okay.

Speaker 2: All right, you're all set.

Speaker 1: All right, thank you.

Speaker 2: You're welcome, sir.

Speaker 1: You have a good day.

Speaker 2: You too.
